<H2>Internet Protocols</H2> 

Session Initiation Protocol</a> (SIP, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2543.txt>RFC 2543</a>, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2543.txt>RFC 3261</a>), 
Session Description Protocol</a> (SDP, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2327.txt>RFC 2327</a>), 
Session Announcement Protocol (SAP, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2974.txt>RFC 2974</a>), 
Protocol Independent Multicast-Sparse Mode (PIM-SM, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2362.txt>RFC 2362</a>), 
TCP-Friendly Rate Control (TFRC, 
<A href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3448.txt">RFC 3448</a>),
Multicast-Scope Zone Announcement Protocol (MZAP, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2776.txt>RFC 2776</a>), 
Multicast Address Allocation (<a
href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2908.txt>RFC 2908</a>, 
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2909.txt>RFC 2909</a>), 
TCP Congestion Window Validation (
<a href=http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2861.txt>RFC 2861</a>),
Reliable Multicast (
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3451.txt">RFC 3451</a>,
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3452.txt">RFC 3452</a>, 
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3453.txt">RFC 3453</a>,
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3048.txt">RFC 3048</a>),
Datagram Congestion Control Protocol (
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4340.txt">RFC 4340</a>,
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4336.txt">RFC 4336</a>),
Multipath TCP (
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc6824.txt">RFC 6824</a>,
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc6356.txt">RFC 6356</a>,
<a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc6182.txt">RFC 6182</a>).

